      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:6:8:32:2",
      "text": [
        " قَالَ أَبُو جَعْفَرٍ ( عليه السلام ) الْحِنَّاءُ يَشْعَلُ الشَّيْبَ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Abu Ali Al Ashary, from Muhammad Bin Abdul Jabbar, from Safwan, from Al A’ala, from Muhammad Bin Muslim who said, ",
          "‘Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘The henna ignites the greying’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "2. Abu Ali al-Ash‘ariy has narrated from Muhammad ibn ‘Abd al-Jabbar from Safwan from al-‘Ala’ from Muhammad ibn Muslim who has said the following: “Abu Ja‘far, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Applying hair dye with henna stirs up gray hairs.’” "
        ]
      }
